<p>For his work on dimorphism, CD asks WAL if he can send roots of two forms of <hi rend="italic">Epilobium angustifolium</hi>. He doubts that they are reciprocally connected like the two forms of <hi rend="italic">Primula</hi>, but will try the experiment.</p> 
